"Run Till It's Dark" is an episode of The Dick Powell Show. It starred Tuesday Weld and Fabian; the latter was cast off the back of the strength of his performance in "A Lion Walks Among Us" on Bus Stop.Hal Humphrey of the Los Angeles Times called it the worst drama in an anthology series for 1962. "To this day, no one has figured out what the drama was about."


